#!/bin/bash
cat << 'REMINDER'
POST-AGENT CHECKLIST — run if you just changed code:
1. requesting-code-review skill
2. code-simplifier on changed files
3. check new code matches existing file conventions
4. update docs/README if behaviour changed
5. update project CLAUDE.md/AGENTS.md if structure changed
6. security-review if auth/API/data/deps changed
7. legal risk check → docs/legal-notes.md (warn, no block)
8. a11y check if frontend changed
9. verify + run + playwright if frontend changed
10. lint + typecheck + tests (retry flaky once)
11. clean_gone after any branch merge
12. git add → commit → push
REMINDER
